data.description: Hurry! This custom built, one-owner home feels like a country estate in the city. It’s loaded with extra amenities to make your life easy, and the homeowner assn. offers trails, a pool and clubhouse. The second-level bedroom studio is a bonus.  From the spacious rooms and wood stove, to the great all-season room, this home has so much to offer! It sports a new roof, new flooring, fresh paint, super storage, even an in-ground sprinkler system.  It’s ready for new owners.  Tour it today!
